er of Manas]] (13 June 2019)<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/global/2019-06/14/content_37480672.htm|title=Xi honored for building Kyrgyz ties|last=An|first=Baijie|last2=Cao|first2=Desheng|date=14 June 2019|newspaper=[[China Daily]]|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=7 September 2019}}</ref>\n* {{flagu|Tajikistan}}: Order of the Crown (15 June 2019)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.ru/world/si-czinpin-nagrazhdyon-vysshim-ordenom-tadzhikistana/|title=|last=|first=|date=15 June 2019|newspaper=[[NEWSru]]|language=ru|script-title=ru:\u0421\u0438 \u0426\u0437\u0438\u043d\u044c\u043f\u0438\u043d \u043d\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0434\u0451\u043d \u0432\u044b\u0441\u0448\u0438\u043c \u043e\u0440\u0434\u0435\u043d\u043e\u043c \u0422\u0430\u0434\u0436\u0438\u043a\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0430|trans-title=Xi Jinping awarded the highest order of Tajikistan|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905163817/https://news.ru/world/si-czinpin-nagrazhdyon-vysshim-ordenom-tadzhikistana/|archive-date=5 September 2019|access-date=5 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n; Key to the City\n* {{flagdeco|US}}{{flagicon|Iowa}} [[Muscatine, Iowa]], U.S. (26 April 1985)<ref name=\"National Public Radio2\">{{cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2012/02/14/146888717/iowa-a-top-destination-for-chinas-vice-president/|title=A Familiar Face Back in Iowa: China's Vice President|last=|first=|date=14 February 2012|newspaper=[[NPR]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714065854/https://www.npr.org/2012/02/14/146888717/iowa-a-top-destination-for-chinas-vice-president|archive-date=14 July 2019|access-date=7 September 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-17022158|title=The early adventures of Xi Jinping|last=Dailey|first=Kate|date=15 February 2012|newspaper=[[BBC News]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331084433/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-17022158|archive-date=31 Ma